3296 // Transfer parms vector element to gui elements
3297 void US_AnaprofPan2DSA::parms_to_gui( int rowx )
3298 {
3299  US_AnaProfile* currProf = &mainw->currProf;
3300  QVector< US_AnaProfile::AnaProf2DSA::Parm2DSA >*
3301  parms = &currProf->ap2DSA.parms;
3302  int kchan = currProf->pchans.count();
3303  int kparm = currProf->ap2DSA.parms.size();
3304 DbgLv(1) << "2D:SL-pg: rowx" << rowx << "kchan" << kchan << "kparm" << kparm;
3305  if ( rowx >= kparm )
3306  {
3307 DbgLv(1) << "2D:SL-pg: *ERROR* rowx>=kparm";
3308  return;
3309  }
3310  US_AnaProfile::AnaProf2DSA::Parm2DSA
3311  parm1 = parms->at( rowx );
3312  le_smin ->setText( QString::number( parm1.s_min ) );
3313  le_smax ->setText( QString::number( parm1.s_max ) );
3314  le_kmin ->setText( QString::number( parm1.k_min ) );
3315  le_kmax ->setText( QString::number( parm1.k_max ) );
3316  le_constk->setText( QString::number( parm1.ff0_const ) );
3317  le_sgrpts->setText( QString::number( parm1.s_grpts ) );
3318  le_kgrpts->setText( QString::number( parm1.k_grpts ) );
3319  le_grreps->setText( QString::number( parm1.gridreps ) );
3320  le_custmg->setText( parm1.cust_grid );
3321  QString chan = parm1.channel;
3322  QString chan_l = sl_chnsel[ rowx ];
3323 DbgLv(1) << "2D:SL-pg: rowx" << rowx << "channel" << chan << chan_l;
3324  if ( chan != chan_l )
3325  { // Parms channel wrong, so replace with correct string
3326  parm1.channel = chan_l;
3327  currProf->ap2DSA.parms.replace( rowx, parm1 );
3328 DbgLv(1) << "2D:SL-pg: chan replaced:" << parms->at( rowx ).channel;
3329  chan = chan_l;
3330  }
3331  int ixchns = cb_chnsel->findText( chan );
3332  if ( ixchns < 0 )
3333  { // Channel string not found, so search for starting substring
3334  for ( int ii = 0; ii < cb_chnsel->count(); ii++ )
3335  {
3336  if ( cb_chnsel->itemText( ii ).startsWith( chan ) )
3337  {
3338  ixchns = ii;
3339 DbgLv(1) << "2D:SL-pg: ixchns(I)" << ixchns << chan << cb_chnsel->itemText(ii);
3340  break;
3341  }
3342  }
3343  }
3344 else
3345  DbgLv(1) << "2D:SL-pg: ixchns(X)" << ixchns << chan << cb_chnsel->itemText(ixchns);
3346  cb_chnsel->setCurrentIndex( ixchns );
3347 
3348  pb_nextch->setEnabled( rowx < ( sl_chnsel.count() - 1 ) );
3349 
3350 }

3914 // Transfer parms vector element to gui elements
3915 void US_AnaprofPanPCSA::parms_to_gui( int rowx )
3916 {
3917  US_AnaProfile* currProf = &mainw->currProf;
3918  QVector< US_AnaProfile::AnaProfPCSA::ParmPCSA >*
3919  parms = &currProf->apPCSA.parms;
3920  int kchan = currProf->pchans.count();
3921  int kparm = currProf->apPCSA.parms.size();
3922 DbgLv(1) << "PC:SL-pg: rowx" << rowx << "kchan" << kchan << "kparm" << kparm;
3923  if ( rowx >= kparm )
3924  {
3925 DbgLv(1) << "PC:SL-pg: *ERROR* rowx>=kparm";
3926  return;
3927  }
3928  US_AnaProfile::AnaProfPCSA::ParmPCSA
3929  parm1 = parms->at( rowx );
3930  QString chan = parm1.channel;
3931  QString chan_g = cb_chnsel->itemText( rowx );
3932  QString chan_l = sl_chnsel[ rowx ];
3933 DbgLv(1) << "PC:SL-pg: rowx" << rowx << "channel" << chan_g << chan << chan_l;
3934 
3935  int ixcurv = cb_curvtype->findText( parm1.curv_type );
3936  if ( ixcurv < 0 )
3937  { // Curve type not found, so search for starting substring
3938  for ( int ii = 0; ii < cb_curvtype->count(); ii++ )
3939  {
3940  if ( cb_curvtype->itemText( ii ).startsWith( parm1.curv_type ) )
3941  {
3942  ixcurv = ii;
3943 DbgLv(1) << "PC:SL-pg: ixcurv" << ixcurv << parm1.curv_type << cb_curvtype->itemText(ii);
3944  break;
3945  }
3946  }
3947  }
3948 
3949  if ( chan != chan_g )
3950  { // Parms channel wrong, so replace with correct string
3951  parm1.channel = chan_g;
3952  currProf->apPCSA.parms.replace( rowx, parm1 );
3953 DbgLv(1) << "PC:SL-pg: chan replaced:" << parms->at( rowx ).channel;
3954  chan = chan_g;
3955  }
3956 
3957  int ixchns = cb_chnsel->findText( chan );
3958  if ( ixchns < 0 )
3959  { // Channel string not found, so search for starting substring
3960  for ( int ii = 0; ii < cb_chnsel->count(); ii++ )
3961  {
3962  if ( cb_chnsel->itemText( ii ).startsWith( chan ) )
3963  {
3964  ixchns = ii;
3965 DbgLv(1) << "PC:SL-pg: ixchns(I)" << ixchns << chan << cb_chnsel->itemText(ii);
3966  break;
3967  }
3968  }
3969  }
3970 else
3971  DbgLv(1) << "PC:SL-pg: ixchns(X)" << ixchns << chan << cb_chnsel->itemText(ixchns);
3972 
3973  le_xmin ->setText( QString::number( parm1.x_min ) );
3974  le_xmax ->setText( QString::number( parm1.x_max ) );
3975  le_ymin ->setText( QString::number( parm1.y_min ) );
3976  le_ymax ->setText( QString::number( parm1.y_max ) );
3977  le_zvalue ->setText( QString::number( parm1.z_value ) );
3978  le_regalpha->setText( QString::number( parm1.tr_alpha ) );
3979  le_varcount->setText( QString::number( parm1.varcount ) );
3980  le_grfiters->setText( QString::number( parm1.grf_iters ) );
3981  le_crpoints->setText( QString::number( parm1.creso_pts ) );
3982  le_mciters ->setText( QString::number( parm1.mc_iters ) );
